
1 - Welcome message

2 - explain user how it works

3 - ask user to input message to encrypt

4 - tell user that now his message is safe

5 - ask user to decrypt message  


CODE 

message = input("Please enter the message yout would like to encrypt")

encryption_key = "sadfsgdgdasrewrafasfdgsdgasfsansaknsadnsadndfsbnsd"

encrypt_message = ""

for i in message: 
	position = encryption_key.find(i)
	newposition = position + 3
	encrypt_message+=encryption_key[newposition]
print(encrypt_message)



